

   OMD - the Open Monitoring Distribution (Naemon Core Edition)
      <http://omdistro.org/> - <http://labs.consol.de

The OMD New Cores Edition is a test and integration platform based on
OMD for Naemon. APIs have changed, new Livestatus implementations have
been build, so this build makes it easier to test the new cores with
Thruk and Mod-Gearman.


What OMD-NC contains in addition
--------------------------------

  * Naemon
  * Livestatus for Naemon
  * Mod-Gearman for Naemon
  * PNP for Naemon
  * Best Practices:
    - Thruk
      - set as default gui
      - autostart enabled
      - enable cookie authentication
    - Naemon
      - enabled by default

